---
import "../assets/index.css";
---

<section class="content-section process-section">
    <div class="section-shell">
        <p class="section-kicker">Tu socio experto</p>
        <h2>Cómo funciona TRT</h2>
        
        <div class="process-flow-container">
            <div class="process-grid">
                <article class="process-step" data-step="1">
                    <div class="step-visual">
                        <div class="step-icon-wrapper">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="step-icon">
                                <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="step-number-badge">01</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Dinos qué necesitas</h3>
                        <p>Comparte marca, medida o foto por WhatsApp. Recibimos listas completas.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="process-step" data-step="2">
                    <div class="step-visual">
                        <div class="step-icon-wrapper">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="step-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="step-number-badge">02</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Cotización Express</h3>
                        <p>Validamos existencia y opciones equivalentes en menos de 10 minutos.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="process-step" data-step="3">
                    <div class="step-visual">
                        <div class="step-icon-wrapper">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="step-icon">
                                <rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"></rect>
                                <polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"></polygon>
                                <circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle>
                                <circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="step-number-badge">03</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Recoges o enviamos</h3>
                        <p>Entrega inmediata local o envío nacional el mismo día a todo México.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
